### =====================================================
### Auth / ownership errors
### =====================================================

### 10. No token – should return 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/stress/samples
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "{{veteranId}}",
  "timestamp_utc": "2026-02-25T08:00:00Z",
  "window_minutes": 5,
  "mean_hr": 72.4,
  "rmssd_ms": 38.7
}

### 11. user_id does not match authenticated user – should return 403
POST {{baseUrl}}/stress/samples
Authorization: Bearer {{veteranToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "timestamp_utc": "2026-02-25T08:00:00Z",
  "window_minutes": 5,
  "mean_hr": 72.4,
  "rmssd_ms": 38.7
}

### =====================================================
### Input errors – should return 400
### =====================================================

### 13. Empty body – should return 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/stress/samples
Authorization: Bearer {{veteranToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 14. Unknown field – should return 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/stress/samples
Authorization: Bearer {{veteranToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "{{veteranId}}",
  "timestamp_utc": "2026-02-25T08:00:00Z",
  "window_minutes": 5,
  "mean_hr": 72.4,
  "rmssd_ms": 38.7,
  "unknown_field": "oops"
}


